net.allwebdesign.common.lib.ui
Class AppModel

java.lang.Object
  net.allwebdesign.common.lib.ui.AppModel

public class AppModel
extends Object

This class enriches Models with additional info used later on to e.g. in views The info includes:
a) User information retrieved from the database and carried on a CustomUserDetailsService object
b) Application properties held in the database and carried on a ApplicationProperties object

Author:
George Moraitakis
